title: Qatar Mining Production
description: Mining production in Qatar increased 7.30 percent in August of 2022 over the same month in the previous year. Mining Production in Qatar averaged -0.78 percent from 2018 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 8.46 percent in July of 2022 and a record low of -13.74 percent in February of 2022. This page provides - Qatar Mining Production- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Qatar Statistics Authority
